data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER**LISTED WAY UNDER MARKET VALUE. Exceptionally well maintained 4 bedroom 2 bath home in Godley. This home has so much to offer you won’t be able to resist. Updated and open concept kitchen and living room. Master is separated from other rooms a with a huge walk in closet that leads straight to the laundry room! Large bedroom or office on the opposite side of the house that could function for whatever you needed. Two other rooms are together in the hallway and share the second bathroom. Offers and an amazing .5 acre lot with a massive fenced in backyard perfect for your kids to live their best life or amazing for entertaining guest! The garage looks like a 2 car from the exterior however, inside it is actually a three with its tandem set up, perfect to store that third car or the boat you have always wanted! Come and check out this beautiful home.  If you use preferred lender up to 1% in closing cost paid.
